data.description: BRAND NEW AC UNIT JUST INSTALLED! NO HOA! NOT A FLOOD ZONE! Looking for some elbow room close to the city? This Concrete Block 3/2 split floor plan boasts cathedral ceilings, laminate flooring & inside laundry all on an 1 Acre+ in Hammock Ridge just off Archer Road. ROOF replaced in June 2021, Well Pump Replaced in March 2020 and Septic pumped in 2019. Direct route to Shands, VA, UF and Downtown Gainesville FL. With a little personalization  this could be a showplace! Make your private appointment today!
